"{\"uid\": \"businesstoday.in-trending-entertainment-story-wish-this-was-true-i-just-need-to-work-on-the-skill-set-now-actor-adil-hussain-reacts-to-mistaken-identity-with-turkish-olympic-shooter-yusuf-dikec-440037-2024-08-03\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home  Market  BT TV  Reels  Menu  Versatile actor Adil Hussain recently found himself in an amusing situation when a fan mistakenly congratulated him for winning a silver medal at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 50, \"end\": 62, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adil_Hussain\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adil Hussain\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adil_Hussain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adil_Hussain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The confusion arose due to a resemblance between the actor and Turkish Olympic shooter Yusuf Dikec.\", \"from\": 200, \"to\": 299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 263, \"end\": 270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_people\", \"score\": 0.7402834328246103, \"rank\": 0.3500800826115266, \"text\": \"Turkish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_people\"}, {\"begin\": 271, \"end\": 286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shooting_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympic shooter\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shooting_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shooting_at_the_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 287, \"end\": 292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"score\": 0.948062537411127, \"rank\": 0.05402384946067227, \"text\": \"Yusuf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The incident came to light when a social media user shared a collage of Adil Hussain and Yusuf Dikec, extending their congratulations to the actor for his supposed Olympic feat.\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adil_Hussain\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adil Hussain\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adil_Hussain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adil_Hussain\"}, {\"begin\": 390, \"end\": 395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"score\": 0.948062537411127, \"rank\": 0.05402384946067227, \"text\": \"Yusuf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Congratulations sir @_AdilHussain on winning silver at Olympics 2024 for Turkey.\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 553, \"end\": 559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9928424790639532, \"rank\": 0.007141187832333908, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Respect (sic),\\\" the fan tweeted.\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The tweet quickly gained traction, catching the attention of the actor himself.\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wish this was true... May be it's not to late to start practicing...\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 743, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since I have the attitude need to work on the skill set now..\\ud83d\\ude06https://t.co/GS8iHQafCg  With his signature wit, Adil responded to the tweet, expressing his desire to make the imaginary achievement a reality.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He wrote, \\\"Wish this was true.\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 981, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe it's not too late to start practicing...\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since I have the attitude, I just need to work on the skill set now.\\\"\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1098, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After the post went viral, the actor told Hindustan Times that the social media user did it on purpose.\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hindustan_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hindustan Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hindustan_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hindustan_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think the tweet was a misunderstanding.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was done deliberately as a joke, so I wasn't surprised when I saw it.\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I actually found it really funny and amusing,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1382, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the work front, Adil is currently starring in 'Ulajh' with Janhvi Kapoor and Gulshan Deviah.\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1447, \"end\": 1453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janhvi_Kapoor\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Janhvi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janhvi_Kapoor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janhvi_Kapoor\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The film was released in theaters on August 2.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1526, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025 Living Media India Limited.\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1572, \